# Text Summarization Tool

## 📌 Overview
This project is part of my internship task. It is a **Text Summarization Tool** built using Natural Language Processing (NLP) techniques.  
The tool takes lengthy text as input and generates a concise summary.

## ⚙️ Features
- Summarizes long articles or paragraphs.
- Uses pre-trained models (`facebook/bart-large-cnn`) from Hugging Face.
- Outputs clear, readable summaries.

## 🚀 How to Run
1. Clone or download this project folder.
2. Install dependencies:
   ```bash
   pip install -r requirements.txt
